.welcome-heading{
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-size: 1.5rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--text-heading);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    margin: 0 0 8px;
    text-align: center;
}

.welcome-message{
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    color: var(--text-body);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0 0 28px;
    font-style: italic;
    max-width: 320px;
}

.iskrib-word{
    font-family: "Playfair Display", serif;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--accent-amber);
    font-style: normal;
}

.welcome-cta{
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    border: none;
    background: var(--accent-dark);
    color: var(--bg-primary);
    font-family: var(--font-ui);
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: transform 0.15s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
}
.welcome-cta:hover{
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
}
.welcome-cta:active{
    transform: translateY(0);
}

/* ── Dark mode ── */
[data-theme="dark"] .welcome-message-child-container{
    box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
}
[data-theme="dark"] .welcome-cta{
    background: var(--accent-amber);
    color: #1A1612;
}
[data-theme="dark"] .welcome-cta:hover{
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(212, 168, 83, 0.25);
}

/* ── Responsive ── */
@media (max-width: 480px){
    .welcome-message-child-container{
        max-width: 92%;
        padding: 32px 24px;
    }
    .welcome-heading{
        font-size: 1.35rem;
    }
    .welcome-message{
        font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
}

@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce){
    .welcome-cta,
    .welcome-close-btn{
        transition: none;
    }
}
```

**Key changes:**
- `position: fixed` instead of `absolute` (so it covers the viewport reliably)
- `var(--bg-backdrop-heavy)` for the overlay instead of `rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.066)` 
- `var(--bg-card)` for the card instead of `rgb(255, 255, 255)` -- automatically adapts to dark mode
- Uses `var(--shadow-modal)` instead of raw box-shadow
- Removes the duplicate `@media(max-width: 428px)` block (was an exact copy)
- Adds dark mode support
- Adds `welcome-cta` button class (mirrors `primary-button` from signup)
- Adds proper close button styling (small, circular, top-right -- matches the profile editor close button pattern from `myprofile.css` line 746)
- Adds `welcome-heading` and `welcome-icon` classes

#### JSX Rewrite for `WelcomeMessage.jsx`

Replace the entire component:

```jsx
import './welcomemessage.css';
import { AnimatePresence, motion } from 'framer-motion';
import confetti from "canvas-confetti";
import { useEffect } from 'react';

const WelcomeMessage = ({ onClose }) => {
    useEffect(() => {
        const canvas = document.getElementById('my-confetti');
        const myConfetti = confetti.create(canvas, { resize: true });

        const timer = setTimeout(() => {
            myConfetti({
                particleCount: 80,
                spread: 100,
                startVelocity: 25,
                ticks: 500,
                gravity: 0.6,
                scalar: 1.2,
                origin: { x: 0.5, y: 0.4 },
                colors: ['#D4A853', '#C4943E', '#E0BA6A', '#FAF9F6', '#8A9E7A']
            });
        }, 500);

        return () => clearTimeout(timer);
    }, []);

    return (
        <>
            <canvas id="my-confetti" className="confetti-layer"></canvas>
            <AnimatePresence>
                <div className="welcome-message-container">
                    <motion.div
                        initial={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 12 }}
                        animate={{
                            opacity: 1,
                            scale: 1,
                            y: 0,
                            transition: {
                                type: "spring",
                                stiffness: 200,
                                damping: 20,
                                duration: 0.4
                            }
                        }}
                        exit={{ opacity: 0, scale: 0.95, y: 8, transition: { type: "tween", duration: 0.2 } }}
                        className="welcome-message-child-container"
                    >
                        {/* Small close X — top right */}
                        <div onClick={onClose} className="welcome-close-btn" aria-label="Close">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
                                <path d="m256-200-56-56 224-224-224-224 56-56 224 224 224-224 56 56-224 224 224 224-56 56-224-224-224 224Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>

                        {/* Pen/quill icon — writing-themed, uses gold accent */}
                        <div className="welcome-icon">
                            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="48" height="48" viewBox="0 -960 960 960" fill="currentColor">
                                <path d="M200-200h57l391-391-57-57-391 391v57Zm-80 80v-170l528-527q12-11 26.5-17t30.5-6q16 0 31 6t26 18l55 56q12 11 17.5 26t5.5 30q0 16-5.5 30.5T817-647L290-120H120Zm640-584-56-56 56 56Zm-141 85-28-29 57 57-29-28Z" />
                            </svg>
                        </div>

                        <h2 className="welcome-heading">You're all set</h2>

                        <p className="welcome-message">
                            Your thoughts now have a home on <span className="iskrib-word">Iskrib</span>. 
                            The blank page awaits.
                        </p>

                        <button onClick={onClose} className="welcome-cta">
                            Begin writing
                        </button>
                    </motion.div>
                </div>
            </AnimatePresence>
        </>
    );
};

export default WelcomeMessage;
```

**Key changes:**
- **Replaced the party popper SVG** (100+ lines of colorful paths) with a clean Material pen/edit icon (same icon system already used throughout the app -- see the close button SVGs in `ProfileEditModal.jsx`). Only 1 path, colored via `currentColor` from the `.welcome-icon` class which uses `--accent-amber`.
- **Replaced the 54px filled-square close button** with a small 18px X icon in a circular hover target, positioned top-right. Reuses the exact same SVG path and hover pattern as the profile editor close button.
- **Added a proper CTA button** ("Begin writing") that calls `onClose`. Styled with `.welcome-cta` which mirrors the `.primary-button` from signup.
- **Updated copy** from the quoted third-person message to a more editorial "You're all set" heading + "Your thoughts now have a home on Iskrib. The blank page awaits." -- literary, warm, on-brand.
- **Added gold-tinted confetti colors** (`colors: ['#D4A853', '#C4943E', '#E0BA6A', '#FAF9F6', '#8A9E7A']`) instead of default rainbow. These are the accent amber, its variants, the cream background, and the sage accent -- all from the design system.
- **Softened the spring animation** from `stiffness: 180` to `200`, and changed `initial` from `scale: 0` (which looks like it pops from nothing) to `scale: 0.95, y: 12` (a gentle reveal, matching the card entry pattern used elsewhere).

