### Change 5: Visual Flow Continuity

After these changes, the three consecutive screens share one design language:

| Screen | Background | Card Style | Typography | Accent |
|--------|-----------|-----------|------------|--------|
| Signup | `--bg-primary` | `--bg-card`, `--border-card`, `--shadow-card-sm` | Playfair title, Lora subtitle, Outfit UI | `--accent-amber` gold focus rings |
| Profile Setup | `--bg-backdrop-heavy` overlay | `--bg-card`, `--border-card`, `--shadow-modal` | Playfair title, Lora subtitle, Outfit inputs | `--accent-amber` gold focus rings |
| Welcome | `--bg-backdrop-heavy` overlay | `--bg-card`, `--border-card`, `--shadow-modal` | Playfair heading, Lora message, Outfit button | `--accent-amber` icon, gold confetti |

All three now flow naturally as variations of the same editorial card pattern.

